<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>統合学力診断・進路判定シミュレーター | 教育支援情報システム</title>
<script src="https://accounts.google.com/gsi/client" async defer></script>
<style>
  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --bg: #f4f7f9;
    --primary: #2c3e50;
    --primary-light: #34495e;
    --accent: #1a5276;
    --border: #b8c4cc;
    --border-light: #d5dde3;
    --text: #1a2530;
    --text-muted: #5a6a7a;
    --text-light: #8a9aa8;
    --white: #ffffff;
    --row-alt: #edf1f5;
    --success: #1a6e3a;
    --warning: #7a4f00;
    --warning-bg: #fff8e6;
    --info-bg: #eaf2fb;
    --danger: #8b1a1a;
    --danger-bg: #fdf0f0;
    --header-h: 48px;
    --nav-h: 38px;
  }

  body {
    font-family: "Meiryo", "メイリオ", "MS Gothic", "ＭＳ ゴシック", sans-serif;
    font-size: 13px;
    background: var(--bg);
    color: var(--text);
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  #header {
    background: var(--primary);
    height: var(--header-h);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 16px;
    gap: 12px;
    border-bottom: 2px solid #1a2a38;
    position: sticky;
    top: 0;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  #header .logo-mark {
    width: 28px; height: 28px;
    background: #fff;
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 11px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    border: 1px solid #aaa;
    letter-spacing: -0.5px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  #header .site-title {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 0.03em;
    flex: 1;
    white-space: nowrap;
    overflow: hidden;
    text-overflow: ellipsis;
  }
  #header .site-title span {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: #a0b8c8;
    font-weight: normal;
    margin-left: 8px;
  }
  #header .header-right {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  #header .sys-time {
    color: #a0b8c8;
    font-size: 11px;
    font-family: "Courier New", monospace;
  }
  #header .user-menu-btn {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    background: none;
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.25);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 4px 10px;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-family: inherit;
    border-radius: 2px;
    position: relative;
  }
  #header .user-menu-btn:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); }
  #header .user-icon {
    width: 22px; height: 22px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: #506070;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 11px;
    overflow: hidden;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  #header .user-icon img { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; }
  #header .caret { font-size: 9px; color: #a0b8c8; }

  /* Dropdown */
  #user-dropdown {
    display: none;
    position: absolute;
    top: calc(var(--header-h) - 2px);
    right: 16px;
    width: 260px;
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 2px 4px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
    z-index: 200;
  }
  #user-dropdown.open { display: block; }
  .dropdown-header {
    background: #e8edf2;
    padding: 8px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-weight: bold;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
  }
  .dropdown-section {
    padding: 10px 12px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .dropdown-section p {
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }
  #google-login-btn {
    width: 100%;
    padding: 7px 10px;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    border: 1px solid #1a2a38;
    cursor: pointer;
    font-size: 12px;
    font-family: inherit;
    text-align: center;
    border-radius: 2px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  #google-login-btn:hover { background: var(--primary-light); }
  #google-login-btn .g-icon {
    width: 16px; height: 16px;
    background: white;
    border-radius: 50%;
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: #4285f4;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .dropdown-note {
    padding: 6px 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-light);
  }
  .dropdown-divider { border: none; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light); margin: 0; }
  .dropdown-link-item {
    display: block;
    padding: 7px 12px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text);
    text-decoration: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: none;
    border: none;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: left;
    font-family: inherit;
  }
  .dropdown-link-item:hover { background: var(--row-alt); }

  /* ── NAV ── */
  #nav {
    background: var(--primary-light);
    height: var(--nav-h);
    display: flex;
    align-items: stretch;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #1e2e3e;
  }
  .nav-item {
    color: #c8d8e4;
    font-size: 12px;
    padding: 0 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    cursor: pointer;
    border-right: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    white-space: nowrap;
    text-decoration: none;
    user-select: none;
  }
  .nav-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: #fff; }
  .nav-item.active { background: var(--bg); color: var(--primary); font-weight: bold; border-bottom: none; }
  .nav-spacer { flex: 1; }
  .nav-right-info {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 0 12px;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: #8aacbc;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .nav-right-info .dot { color: #4a9; }

  /* ── BREADCRUMB ── */
  #breadcrumb {
    padding: 6px 16px;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    background: #ecf0f4;
  }
  #breadcrumb a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  #breadcrumb a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
  #breadcrumb span { margin: 0 4px; color: var(--text-light); }

  /* ── MAIN ── */
  #main {
    padding: 14px 16px 24px;
    max-width: 1280px;
  }

  .page-heading {
    display: flex;
    align-items: baseline;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .page-heading h1 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--primary);
  }
  .page-heading .update-badge {
    font-size: 10px;
    background: var(--primary);
    color: #fff;
    padding: 1px 6px;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }

  /* ── NOTICES ── */
  .notice-list { margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .notice {
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-left: 3px solid transparent;
    font-size: 12px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .notice.info { background: var(--info-bg); border-color: #2471a3; color: #1a4060; }
  .notice.warning { background: var(--warning-bg); border-color: #d4a017; color: var(--warning); }
  .notice.danger { background: var(--danger-bg); border-color: #c0392b; color: var(--danger); }
  .notice .n-tag {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: bold;
    border: 1px solid currentColor;
    padding: 0 4px;
    border-radius: 1px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    opacity: 0.8;
  }
  .notice .n-date { color: inherit; opacity: 0.6; margin-left: auto; font-size: 10px; white-space: nowrap; }

  /* ── GRID ── */
  .grid-2 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .grid-3 { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; }

  /* ── CARD / PANEL ── */
  .panel {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-top: 2px solid var(--primary);
  }
  .panel-head {
    background: #dde4ea;
    padding: 6px 10px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: bold;
    color: var(--primary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
  }
  .panel-head .ph-sub {
    font-size: 10px;
    font-weight: normal;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-left: auto;
  }
  .panel-body { padding: 10px; }

  /* ── STAT TILES ── */
  .stat-tile {
    background: var(--white);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 10px 12px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2px;
  }
  .stat-tile .st-label { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .stat-tile .st-value { font-size: 22px; font-weight: bold; color: var(--primary); line-height: 1; }
  .stat-tile .st-value small { font-size: 12px; font-weight: normal; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .stat-tile .st-sub { font-size: 10px; color: var(--text-light); }
  .stat-tile .st-change { font-size: 10px; }
  .stat-tile .st-change.up { color: var(--success); }
  .stat-tile .st-change.down { color: var(--danger); }

  /* ── TABLE ── */
  table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; font-size: 12px; }
  th {
    background: #dde4ea;
    color: var(--primary);
    padding: 5px 8px;
    text-align: left;
    font-weight: bold;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    white-space: nowrap;
  }
  th.num, td.num { text-align: right; }
  td {
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    color: var(--text);
  }
  tr:nth-child(even) td { background: var(--row-alt); }
  tr:hover td { background: #dce8f2; }
  .rank-badge {
    display: inline-block;
    width: 22px; height: 18px;
    line-height: 18px;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 11px;
    border-radius: 1px;
  }
  .rank-S { background: #c0392b; color: #fff; }
  .rank-A { background: #e67e22; color: #fff; }
  .rank-B { background: #2471a3; color: #fff; }
  .rank-C { background: #27ae60; color: #fff; }
  .rank-D { background: #7f8c8d; color: #fff; }
  .judge-pass { color: var(--success); font-weight: bold; }
  .judge-fail { color: var(--danger); }
  .judge-border { color: #8a6000; font-weight: bold; }

  /* ── SYSTEM STATUS ── */
  .status-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 4px; }
  .status-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 3px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dotted var(--border-light);
    gap: 8px;
    font-size: 11px;
  }
  .status-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .status-row .sr-name { flex: 1; color: var(--text-muted); }
  .status-row .sr-dot {
    width: 8px; height: 8px; border-radius: 50%;
    background: #27ae60;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .status-row .sr-dot.warn { background: #e67e22; }
  .status-row .sr-dot.off { background: #c0392b; }
  .status-row .sr-val { font-family: "Courier New", monospace; color: var(--text); }
  .status-row .sr-status { width: 60px; text-align: right; font-size: 10px; }
  .sr-ok { color: var(--success); }
  .sr-warn { color: #b07800; }

  /* ── CHART BAR (CSS ONLY) ── */
  .bar-chart { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .bar-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px; font-size: 11px; }
  .bar-row .br-label { width: 80px; text-align: right; color: var(--text-muted); white-space: nowrap; overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; }
  .bar-row .br-track { flex: 1; height: 14px; background: #e0e8f0; border: 1px solid var(--border-light); position: relative; }
  .bar-row .br-fill { height: 100%; background: var(--primary); }
  .bar-row .br-fill.sub { background: #5d8aa8; }
  .bar-row .br-val { width: 36px; font-family: "Courier New", monospace; color: var(--text); font-size: 10px; }

  /* ── ALGORITHM LOG ── */
  .log-list { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; font-size: 11px; }
  .log-entry {
    display: flex;
    padding: 4px 6px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    gap: 8px;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
  .log-entry:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .log-entry .le-time { color: var(--text-light); white-space: nowrap; font-family: "Courier New", monospace; }
  .log-entry .le-type {
    font-size: 10px;
    padding: 0 4px;
    border-radius: 1px;
    white-space: nowrap;
    font-weight: bold;
  }
  .le-type.upd { background: #d5e8f8; color: #1a4a70; }
  .le-type.fix { background: #d5f0df; color: #1a5030; }
  .le-type.mnt { background: #f0ead5; color: #5a3a00; }
  .log-entry .le-msg { color: var(--text); flex: 1; }

  /* ── MINI TABLE ── */
  .mini-kv { font-size: 11px; width: 100%; }
  .mini-kv td { padding: 3px 6px; border: 1px solid var(--border-light); }
  .mini-kv td:first-child { background: #e8edf2; color: var(--text-muted); font-weight: bold; width: 40%; }

  /* ── LOADING OVERLAY ── */
  #loading-overlay {
    display: none;
    position: fixed;
    inset: 0;
    background: rgba(20,30,40,0.82);
    z-index: 1000;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 18px;
  }
  #loading-overlay.show { display: flex; }
  .loading-box {
    background: var(--primary);
    border: 1px solid #4a7090;
    padding: 28px 40px;
    text-align: center;
    min-width: 320px;
  }
  .loading-box .lb-title { color: #a0c8e0; font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.08em; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .loading-box .lb-main { color: #fff; font-size: 14px; font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .loading-bar-track {
    height: 4px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
    margin-bottom: 10px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .loading-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: #5dade2;
    animation: loadprog 2.8s linear forwards;
  }
  @keyframes loadprog { 0% { width: 0%; } 85% { width: 90%; } 100% { width: 100%; } }
  .loading-box .lb-sub { color: #6a9ab8; font-size: 10px; font-family: "Courier New", monospace; }
  .lb-dots::after {
    content: '';
    animation: dots 1.2s steps(3, end) infinite;
  }
  @keyframes dots { 0%,100%{content:'.';} 33%{content:'..';} 66%{content:'...';} }

  /* ── FOOTER ── */
  #footer {
    margin-top: 20px;
    padding: 10px 16px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    background: #dde4ea;
    font-size: 10px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
  }
  #footer a { color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none; }
  #footer a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* ── SCROLLBAR ── */
  ::-webkit-scrollbar { width: 8px; height: 8px; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-track { background: #e0e8f0; }
  ::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb { background: #8aaabb; border-radius: 0; }

  /* Responsive clamp */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; }
  }
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .grid-2, .grid-3 { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    #header .sys-time { display: none; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- ══ HEADER ══ -->
<header id="header">
  <div class="logo-mark">教育<br>診断</div>
  <div class="site-title">
    統合学力診断・進路判定シミュレーター
    <span>SADCS ver.4.2.1</span>
  </div>
  <div class="header-right">
    <div class="sys-time" id="sys-clock">--:--:--</div>
    <button class="user-menu-btn" id="user-menu-trigger" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">
      <div class="user-icon" id="user-icon-wrap">
        <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="#a0b8c8"><circle cx="8" cy="5.5" r="3"/><path d="M2 13.5c0-3.3 2.7-5 6-5s6 1.7 6 5"/></svg>
      </div>
      <span id="user-label">ゲスト（ログイン）</span>
      <span class="caret">▼</span>
    </button>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- Dropdown -->
<div id="user-dropdown" role="menu">
  <div class="dropdown-header">利用者メニュー</div>
  <div class="dropdown-section" id="login-section">
    <p>本システムを利用するにはログインが必要です。</p>
    <button id="google-login-btn">
      <span class="g-icon">G</span>
      Googleアカウントでログイン
    </button>
  </div>
  <div class="dropdown-section" id="user-info-section" style="display:none;">
    <div class="mini-kv" style="width:100%;">
      <table>
        <tr><td>利用者名</td><td id="dd-name">—</td></tr>
        <tr><td>メール</td><td id="dd-email" style="font-size:10px;">—</td></tr>
        <tr><td>権限</td><td>一般利用者</td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="dropdown-note">
    ※ 所属機関のアカウントでログインしてください。<br>
    個人アカウントでの利用は管理者の許可が必要です。
  </div>
  <hr class="dropdown-divider">
  <button class="dropdown-link-item">利用マニュアル（PDF）</button>
  <button class="dropdown-link-item">問い合わせ・障害報告</button>
  <button class="dropdown-link-item" id="logout-btn" style="display:none;color:#8b1a1a;">ログアウト</button>
</div>

<!-- ══ NAV ══ -->
<nav id="nav">
  <a class="nav-item active" href="#">ダッシュボード</a>
  <a class="nav-item" href="#">判定シミュレーション</a>
  <a class="nav-item" href="#">模擬試験データ管理</a>
  <a class="nav-item" href="#">合格ライン照合</a>
  <a class="nav-item" href="#">進路指導レポート</a>
  <a class="nav-item" href="#">アルゴリズム設定</a>
  <div class="nav-spacer"></div>
  <div class="nav-right-info">
    <span><span class="dot">●</span> DB接続: 正常</span>
    <span>最終同期: 2026-03-30 07:43</span>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ══ BREADCRUMB ══ -->
<div id="breadcrumb">
  <a href="#">ホーム</a><span>›</span>ダッシュボード
</div>

<!-- ══ MAIN CONTENT ══ -->
<div id="main">

  <!-- Page Heading -->
  <div class="page-heading">
    <h1>学力診断ダッシュボード — 2026年度（令和8年度）</h1>
    <span class="update-badge">2026年度入試データ照合完了</span>
  </div>

  <!-- Notices -->
  <div class="notice-list">
    <div class="notice warning">
      <span class="n-tag">お知らせ</span>
      <span>【重要】2026年度センター試験廃止後の共通テスト配点変更に伴い、判定アルゴリズムを更新しました（v4.2.1 → v4.2.2 予定）。詳細はアルゴリズム設定ページを参照してください。</span>
      <span class="n-date">2026-03-28</span>
    </div>
    <div class="notice info">
      <span class="n-tag">メンテナンス</span>
      <span>定期メンテナンスを 2026年4月5日（土）02:00〜06:00 に実施します。この間、本システムはご利用いただけません。</span>
      <span class="n-date">2026-03-25</span>
    </div>
    <div class="notice danger">
      <span class="n-tag">障害</span>
      <span>3月27日 14:30〜15:10 のデータ同期に遅延が発生しました。該当時間帯の判定結果は再計算済みです。</span>
      <span class="n-date">2026-03-27</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- KPI Tiles -->
  <div class="grid-3" style="margin-bottom:12px;">
    <div class="stat-tile">
      <div class="st-label">登録生徒数（2026年度）</div>
      <div class="st-value">4,218 <small>名</small></div>
      <div class="st-sub">前年度比 <span class="st-change up">▲ 312名</span></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-tile">
      <div class="st-label">判定実施件数（今月）</div>
      <div class="st-value">18,743 <small>件</small></div>
      <div class="st-sub">1日あたり平均: 714.5件</div>
    </div>
